      "content": "Subject: Sincere Apology and Special Offer for Your Espresso Machine Delay\n\nDear [Customer's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to extend my sincerest apologies for the delay in the shipment of your recently purchased espresso machine. I understand how important this purchase is to you, and I truly regret any inconvenience this may have caused.\n\nRecently, we experienced an unexpected glitch in our logistics system, which resulted in a delay that we did not anticipate. Despite our best efforts to maintain smooth operations, this was a rare and unfortunate occurrence that temporarily affected our ability to deliver your order on time.\n\nTo make amends, we would like to offer you a 15% discount on your next purchase with us. Alternatively, we can expedite your current order at no additional cost, ensuring that you receive your espresso machine as soon as possible.\n\nWe value your business and appreciate your understanding in this matter. Once again, I apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused, and I thank you for your patience as we work to resolve this issue.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]",
